rticle class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/april-cyber-legends.php" title="Cybersecurity Veteran: \xe2\x80\x98The Most Memorable Moment in My Career Was When I Finally Realized I Can Do What I Love\xe2\x80\x99 " class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/april-cyber-legends.jpg" alt="April cyber legends zoom call." style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">Cybersecurity<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/april-cyber-legends.php" title="Cybersecurity Veteran: \xe2\x80\x98The Most Memorable Moment in My Career Was When I Finally Realized I Can Do What I Love\xe2\x80\x99 ">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">Cybersecurity Veteran: \xe2\x80\x98The Most Memorable Moment in My Career Was When I Finally Realized I Can Do What I Love\xe2\x80\x99 </h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Roger Grimes, a data-driven defense evangelist and security consultant for KnowBe4, Inc., recently shared his advice with the next generation of cybersecurity professionals as part of the University\xe2\x80\x99s Connecticut Institute of Technology\xe2\x80\x99s Cyber Legends Series. </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/releases/2021/karl-minges-health-grant.php" title="Health Services Researcher Earns First National Institutes of Health Grant in University History" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/2021/karl-minges-full.png" alt="University of New Haven Campus" style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">University Professor Makes History<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/releases/2021/karl-minges-health-grant.php" title="Health Services Researcher Earns First National Institutes of Health Grant in University History">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">University News</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">Health Services Researcher Earns First National Institutes of Health Grant in University History</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Karl Minges, Ph.D., MPH, is passionate about improving the health of vulnerable populations, and an award for nearly $450,000 from the National Institutes of Health \xe2\x80\x93 the University\xe2\x80\x99s first \xe2\x80\x93 will enable him to advance his important work.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/stem-international-womens-day.php" title="Virtual Event Fosters Community, Connection, and Celebration of Women in STEM" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/horvat.jpg" alt="Kristine Horvat, Ph.D." style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">Women in STEM<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/stem-international-womens-day.php" title="Virtual Event Fosters Community, Connection, and Celebration of Women in STEM">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">Virtual Event Fosters Community, Connection, and Celebration of Women in STEM</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Kristine Horvat, Ph.D., the first member of her family to pursue a career in the STEM fields of science, technology, engineering, and math, helped organize an event to share her passion for STEM with young women. </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/hannah-providence-founders-day.php" title="What Founder\'s Day Means to Me" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/founders-day-hp.jpg" alt="Hannah Providence \'22" style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">Founder\'s Day<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/hannah-providence-founders-day.php" title="What Founder\'s Day Means to Me">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">What Founder\'s Day Means to Me</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">This year, Founders Day was particularly meaningful, as it was a fun and engaging way for the University community to safely come together to commemorate the University\xe2\x80\x99s 101st birthday, as well as celebrate our resilience and Charger pride.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/michelle-alexander.php" title="Bestselling Author Tells University Community: \xe2\x80\x98I Hope We Dream Big and Don\xe2\x80\x99t Settle\xe2\x80\x99" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/michelle-alexander-speaker.png" alt="Michelle Alexander recently spoke to the University community." style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">\'Dream Big and Don\'t Settle\'<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/michelle-alexander.php" title="Bestselling Author Tells University Community: \xe2\x80\x98I Hope We Dream Big and Don\xe2\x80\x99t Settle\xe2\x80\x99">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">Bestselling Author Tells University Community: \xe2\x80\x98I Hope We Dream Big and Don\xe2\x80\x99t Settle\xe2\x80\x99</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Michelle Alexander, a civil rights lawyer, advocate, and author of an award-winning book that inspired a national conversation about mass incarceration, spoke to the University community following the verdict in the Derek Chauvin trial, encouraging students to be courageous.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/psychology-grad.php" title="Class of 2021 Outstanding Psychology Majors Reflect on Time as Chargers" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/psychology-grad.jpg" alt="Alison Klein \'21, Jordan Bernard \xe2\x80\x9921, and Cody Ruais \xe2\x80\x9921. " style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">Psychology<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/psychology-grad.php" title="Class of 2021 Outstanding Psychology Majors Reflect on Time as Chargers">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">Class of 2021 Outstanding Psychology Majors Reflect on Time as Chargers</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Meet three members of the University\xe2\x80\x99s Class of 2021 who will be earn their psychology degrees as part of Spring Commencement. They are looking forward to continuing their education after graduation. </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/covid-fall-2021.php" title="Creating a Culture of Preparation Best Positions University for Success in Fall 2021 \xe2\x80\x93 and Beyond" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/fall-2021-image.jpg" alt="Chargers flag" style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">Charging Into Fall \'21<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/covid-fall-2021.php" title="Creating a Culture of Preparation Best Positions University for Success in Fall 2021 \xe2\x80\x93 and Beyond">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p clas