aven are planning a virtual concert to help support these venues.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/arely-parra-lopez.php" title="First-Generation Student Passionate About Fostering Sense of Belonging" class="news-img">\n                            <img src="/_resources/images/news/non-college-specific/blog/2021/parra-lapez-3.jpg" alt="Arely Parra L\xc3\xb3pez \xe2\x80\x9921" style="height: 200px; width: 100%">\n                            <h3 class="label">First Generation<span class="nhv-rqm"></span></h3>\n                        </a>\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t<a href="/news/blog/2021/arely-parra-lopez.php" title="First-Generation Student Passionate About Fostering Sense of Belonging">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="news-preview">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class="news-category">The Charger Blog</p>\n                                <h3 class="article-title">First-Generation Student Passionate About Fostering Sense of Belonging</h3>\n                                <p class="article-desc">Arely Parra L\xc3\xb3pez \xe2\x80\x9921 will soon become the first member of her family to earn a college degree, and she will be awarded two bachelor\xe2\x80\x99s degrees at the University\xe2\x80\x99s Spring Commencement. She is already looking forward to continuing her education.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a>\n                    </article><!-- /.news -->\n            \n\n        \n                                <article class="news internal list-item" role="article">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                        <a href="/news/blog/2021/thomas-chung.php" title="\xe2\x80\x98\xe2\x80\x98The Stable\xe2\x80\x99 Provides My Teammates and Me with the Best Possible Gaming Experience\xe2\x80\x99" 